Debian/Ubuntu Apt-Get Repository

Xenlism Wildfire support Debian/Ubuntu Base apt-get Repositories.

Following Command line in Terminal.
add sourceforg.net public gnupg key to the APT keys database


	sudo apt-key adv --keyserver keys.gnupg.net --recv-keys 90127F5B


add "deb http://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/xenlism-wildfire/repo deb/" (without qoute) to /etc/apt/sources.list.


	echo "deb http://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/xenlism-wildfire/repo deb/" | sudo tee -a /etc/apt/sources.list
	


Update System and Install Xenlism Wildfire icon theme And Xenlism Artwork Wallpapers.


	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get install xenlism-wildfire-icon-theme
	sudo apt-get install xenlism-artwork-wallpapers
	
